<p>Venezuelan opposition leader María Corina Machado was awarded the 2025 Nobel Peace Prize on Friday for championing democratic rights and fair elections in her country [cbsnews.com#4][nytimes.com#5]. Independent analysts cited by the New York Times say the opposition movement she galvanized won last year’s election, only for the result to be taken by President Nicolás Maduro [nytimes.com#5]. After the announcement, Machado dedicated the prize to Venezuelans and to President Trump, and expressed gratitude for his efforts toward peace [rfi.fr#9][bbc.com#3]. The committee that awards the Nobel Peace Prize is examining whether there was advance knowledge after a sudden surge in bets for Machado on Polymarket, where her odds reportedly jumped from about 3.75% to nearly 73% hours before the news,</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/4VtO0gcsIdE1E6fcjacfczUL_vhEsM7Dj8dA78IzogxXFfTZVanHiHqaVP92xdWhRNAn68g5i3ol8w2b4HGWC4L4_FNmXsl_mm2JvP578zdhrTW0YlDalKSpcgN_QuuwsAruHsjOT2GhGfGfbdkkNSNpAnswvWHl1fsBK0qxFGxB0UX1yRlpJ5K8EftLF2cg' alt='María Corina Machado during the opening rally for the Presidential campaign last year in Caracas.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Prize rationale: The Nobel recognition highlighted her work &quot;keeping the flame of democracy burning amid growing darkness&quot; as she has fought for fair elections in Venezuela [cbsnews.com#4].</li><li>Election backdrop: Independent analysts say the opposition she helped mobilize won last year’s election, which they say was then taken by President Nicolás Maduro [nytimes.com#5].</li><li>Dedication and thanks: Machado dedicated the prize to Venezuelans and to President Trump, telling him she was grateful for &quot;what he&#x27;s doing... around the world for peace&quot; [rfi.fr#9][bbc.com#3].</li><li>Betting surge probe: Nobel organizers are looking into whether there was advance knowledge after Polymarket odds for Machado leapt from about 3.75% to nearly 73% just hours beforehand [nytimes.com#6][firstpost.com#2].</li><li>Criticism noted: She faces criticism from some over her support for U.S.-led sanctions on Venezuela, even as supporters praise her pro-democracy stance [thehindu.com#1][ndtv.com#8].</li></ul><blockquote>What he&#x27;s doing... around the world for peace - María Corina Machado</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>María Corina Machado: Dedicated the prize to Venezuelans and to President Trump, expressing gratitude for his efforts toward peace. (<a href='https://www.rfi.fr/en/international/20251011-venezuela-s-machado-dedicates-nobel-peace-prize-to-fellow-citizens-and-trump'>RFI</a>)</li><li>Nobel Prize committee: Said it was looking into whether there was advance knowledge related to a pre-announcement betting surge. (<a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/10/world/nobel-prize-bets-machado-investigation.html'>The New York Times</a>)</li><li>Critics: Questioned the award in light of Machado’s support for U.S.-led sanctions on Venezuela. (<a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/why-nobel-peace-prize-winner-maria-corina-machado-is-facing-criticism-9436325#publisher=newsstand'>NDTV</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/maria-corina-machado-maduros-foe-trumps-friend/article70152997.ece'>Maria Corina Machado | Maduro’s foe, Trump’s friend</a> - thehindu.com</li><li><a href='https://www.firstpost.com/explainers/leak-nobel-peace-prize-2025-maria-corina-machado-13941176.html'>Was the Nobel Peace Prize leaked?</a> - firstpost.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c5y8y25l250o'>We&#x27;re grateful for what Trump is doing for peace, Nobel winner tells BBC</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.cbsnews.com/video/maria-corina-machado-nobel-prize-winner-on-the-fight-for-democracy-in-venezuela/'>María Corina Machado, Nobel Prize winner, on the fight for democracy in Venezuela</a> - cbsnews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/10/world/americas/machado-venezuela-nobel-peace-prize.html'>María Corina Machado Wins Nobel Peace Prize Despite Trump’s Campaign</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/opinion/this-is-really-why-maria-corina-machado-dedicated-her-nobel-peace-prize-to-donald-trump-9436162#publisher=newsstand'>Opinion: Opinion | This Is Really Why Machado &#x27;Dedicated&#x27; Her Nobel To Trump</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.rfi.fr/en/international/20251011-venezuela-s-machado-dedicates-nobel-peace-prize-to-fellow-citizens-and-trump'>Venezuela&#x27;s Machado dedicates Nobel Peace Prize to fellow citizens and Trump</a> - rfi.fr</li></ul>